<Ventura:SmartPage
    x:Class="Demo.StartPage"
    xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
    xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
    xmlns:Ventura="using:Ventura.Controls"
    xmlns:d="http://schemas.microsoft.com/expression/blend/2008"
    xmlns:mc="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/markup-compatibility/2006"
    mc:Ignorable="d">

    <Ventura:SmartPagePanel>

        <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource BaseTextBlockStyle}">Start Page</TextBlock>

        <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap">
            This is the showcase application for Ventura UWP. Ventura UWP is a complete system for the rapid
            development of LOB (Line of Business) software.
        </TextBlock>

        <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap">
            Ventura is a combination of software development framework, control suite, and a 3-tier SQL framework
            for C# projects where database access and web services are integrated into a single solution.
        </TextBlock>

        <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap">
            Ventura is much more than the sum of its parts as all the components are perfectly integrated.
            High productivity and simplicity for the developer, and a modern and super responsive user-interface
            for the end-user.
        </TextBlock>

        <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap">
            With Ventura, a development team with at least average-quality developers
            is able to rapidly produce professional and consistent results.
        </TextBlock>

        <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap">
            Ventura is currently a research project.
        </TextBlock>

        <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap">
            Please visit<Run Text=" " /><Hyperlink NavigateUri="https://venturatools.com">https://venturatools.com</Hyperlink>
            and sign up for my mailing list to receive product announcements.</TextBlock>

        <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap">
            My email address is<Run Text=" " /><Hyperlink NavigateUri="mailto:fvv@venturatools.com">fvv@venturatools.com</Hyperlink>
        </TextBlock>

        <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap">
            Thank you for your interest,<LineBreak />
            Frank Th. van de Ven, the Netherlands.</TextBlock>

    </Ventura:SmartPagePanel>
</Ventura:SmartPage>
